name: Old Grey Kitty Local 94 Loulou
bio: Good morning! I'm Old Grey Kitty Local 94 Loulou. I'm a Culinary Sanitation Specialist by day, and I like talking about how much I lift by night. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their silk scarves and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. I think you'll love me beclaws I have cattitude.
